# About Finovia Bank

Finovia Bank was founded by Laura Singh in 2012 as a digital-first financial institution focused on redefining customer banking through innovation and transparency.
Headquartered in New York, Finovia has grown into a trusted name in fintech banking with over 8 million customers across 15 countries.

The bankâ€™s vision is to make finance simple, accessible, and empowering for individuals and small businesses.
Its flagship services include **DigitalBanking** for online accounts, **SmartLend** for intelligent lending, **SecureVault** for data protection, and **InvestIQ** for smart investing.

By 2025, Finovia employs more than 1,000 people and operates 25 regional hubs worldwide.
